    <h3><a name="3"></a>Nov 06 - Nov 08 (9 posts): <a href="http://docs.FreeBSD.org/cgi/getmsg.cgi?fetch=2406+0+archive/2000/freebsd-advocacy/20001112.freebsd-advocacy">CounterStrike</a></h3>

    <p>This discussion is also continued on from <a href="05.html#3">last
